name: Fantasy Armors
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi

Important information:

As a longtime Monster Hunter fan, I was looking forward to training this model.
I am pleased with the results, as you can see, however the LoRA can be a bit unruly unless you input the following negative prompts:

(((wings))), (((dragon wings))), (((tail))), (((dragon tail)))

Please make sure you are using them, Rathalos is, after all, a dragon shaped wyvern and many non-anime models I've trend do tend to attach inhuman features to my character.

I also recommend you do not go past 0.8 with this.

This LoRA is good, but it has a fiery temper, like Rathalos, please watch out!
